        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>This disbound scrapbook consists of photos, leaflets, flyers, postcards, uniform patches, a poster (folded), and copies of the New Masses. Some post-SCW material memorializing the International Brigades in Mexico. Also included is Friends of the Abraham Lincoln Brigade social service support information for volunteers returning to New York City in 1939.</p>
